{"type": "article", "id": 19938, "title": "琴酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-30T07:20:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607174318V074EbsGwIRTYOCu.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这瓶琴酒的包装设计非常清爽，主要使用了深蓝色和白色。它产自葡萄牙的杜罗河地区，设计者就在包装上用蓝色和波浪线条来提示产地。它的 logo 是Co是名字 COBALTO-17 的缩写，大小写并排的写法也是化学元素的标法。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150305zwR6LZ82y5xvUX3H.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"772\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150306SuI6M1r08kbCtlBY.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"721\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150307axwF6fkKYMn18Cdh.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"721\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150307Roh5d81YL9DNmvQ2.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"721\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}